    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >QQ玩家交流群：755462588</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256450/extras/888c358ced9a1e4162b1ce7546282868.avif?t=1757960780\" width=616 height=190 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主控角色…不存在？！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《夺魄机兵》是一款经典俯视角射击游戏，并融入了类肉鸽元素。游戏启发自《废土之王》（《核子王座》），并进行大胆创新。作为一个没有实体，只为破坏而生的AI程序，你必须夺取敌方机体的控制权——在乱战之中进行无差别的华丽屠戮，直到完成那个神秘的终极目标。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>转移决生死</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以在战斗中随时切换控制的机体，每种机体都有自己独特的武装和玩法，并且有专属的升级库可供选择。《夺魄机兵》不单单是一款射击游戏，它还将考验你的瞬时判断能力，下个宿体该如何选择？被迫放弃当前宿体时又该如何处理？哪部机体最适合当前战况，又该怎么高效地清理房间中的全部敌人？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >              <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256450/extras/0c58997780c787e564b5b7c5c489708d.poster.avif?t=1757960780\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256450/extras/0c58997780c787e564b5b7c5c489708d.webm?t=1757960780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256450/extras/0c58997780c787e564b5b7c5c489708d.mp4?t=1757960780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>后启示录时代降临</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >数码宠物、学生项目、生体模因。在短短一年的时间内，它们就成为了仅剩的智能生命。十年后，只有真正的强者才得以存续，而就在2120年……你经由其手诞生了。距离所有的智能生命全部消失还有多久呢？ <br>在人类世界的残垣败瓦间穿行，挑战数个程序生成的关卡，与居住在其中的古怪机械体展开斗争。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >              <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256450/extras/2f4543103bc643f1f4232d099085e9ff.poster.avif?t=1757960780\" width=480 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256450/extras/2f4543103bc643f1f4232d099085e9ff.webm?t=1757960780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256450/extras/2f4543103bc643f1f4232d099085e9ff.mp4?t=1757960780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>秀出风格</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《夺魄机兵》扩展了《鬼泣》系列和《疯狂连杀》等游戏中的风格系统，将风格点数化作了局内可用的货币。通过掌握战斗机巧和“花式射击”赚取点数来获得各种升级，从而提升甚至改变不同机体的性能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >            <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256450/extras/61faf8fdb69fcc13f570929f27a38aae.poster.avif?t=1757960780\" width=480 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256450/extras/61faf8fdb69fcc13f570929f27a38aae.webm?t=1757960780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256450/extras/61faf8fdb69fcc13f570929f27a38aae.mp4?t=1757960780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
